Process called "windows_arm64_SYS_GETPPID" returns Integer:
    Return -1  Note: Windows has no direct GetParentProcessId; NT-only via NtQueryInformationProcess
End Process

Process called "windows_arm64_SYS_GETUID" returns Integer:
